talent level 10 upgrade Storm Bolt
increase strenght scaling by 50%
increase cast range by 300
increase push force by 100
increase magic resist lost by 9%

add a new modifier Violent Bolt
after hiting the target it will send other storm bolt to near enemy in a radius of 350
of the explosion of the first one and dealing 50% of the damage to the other target as well
if there is no one around storm bolt damage will deal 50% magical and Pure and also dealing 1% of the target max health as damage


SPELL W
Thunder Clap
Muradin Smash the ground, dealing damage and slowing attack speed and movement speed. The more enemy hit
by this spell the more damage it deal and reducing cooldown

